skins.shipDescription: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!
skins.selfIntroduction: The Virtual Maid of Hololive! I'm often called clumsy and careless, but... that's not true!
skins.acquisition: G-Good Aquafternoon...! I'm Minato Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive~ U-Ugh... I didn't know I would have to introduce myself in this outfit!
skins.login: Good Aquafternoon~ I'm going to be playing games for a bit as well, so best of luck with your work, Commander~
skins.details: If I stand on top of this equipment, I'm taller than the Commander! ... Or so it was supposed to be.
skins.secretaryIdle1: I usually wear a maid uniform so this is a bit uncomfortable.
skins.secretaryIdle2: Don't stare at me so much, okay?! I'm really embarrassed!
skins.secretaryIdle3: If you look at me again, I'm going to have you treat me to something tasty!
skins.secretaryTouch: Hm? Did you have something you wanted to request of the strongest maid, me?

skins.shipDescription: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!
skins.acquisition: Commander, good Aquafternoon~! Nice to meet you, it's Aqua, the Gamer Maid from Hololive! I'll show ya what the strongest maid can do!
skins.login: Whew~ I'm glad I didn't sleep in today. Well, what should I do, Commander?
skins.details: I-I'm telling you just this once, so... I sink like a rock in the water, so make sure you support me properly, okay! I'm okay with shallow water, though.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Mas... Commander! It's really confuzzling because I'm not used to calling people that ...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Just because I'm a virtual maid doesn't mean that I'm good at doing all sorts of chores!
skins.secretaryIdle3: In exchange for taking care of chores, feed me tasty sushi~!
skins.secretaryIdle4: Hehehehe, I'll be able to make my broadcast more interesting if I upgrade my equipment! For now, let's set the visual effects to MAX, start this up like so, and ... let's blow everything up!!! ... Eh, an error...? ... Come onNNNNNNNN!!!
skins.secretaryTouch: You wanna play a game with me? I'm super duper strong, so prepare yourself!
